es.csic.iiia.nsm.norm.generation.cbr
Class Case

java.lang.Object
  es.csic.iiia.nsm.norm.generation.cbr.Case

public class Case
extends java.lang.Object

A case of a Case Base. Each case contains:

  1. a CaseDescription that describes a conflicting situation that must be resolved; and
  2. a List of possible solutions (objects CaseSolution) that are aimed to solve the case.

Author:
"Javier Morales (jmorales@iiia.csic.es)"
